  :markdown
    #### Usage

    The above `.sub-topbar` example is achieved by the following

    ~~~haml
    .topbar
      .title Wardrobe
    .sub-topbar
      .left-half
        %form.datepicker
          %input(type="text" value="09/24/2014 - 09/31/2014")
        .breadcrumb
          %ul
            %li
              %span.dropdown
                = link_to "All Parameters", "#"
                %i.icon.down
                %ul
                  %li= link_to "option 1", "#"
                  %li= link_to "option 2", "#"
                  %li= link_to "option 3", "#"
      .right-half.text-right
        = link_to "", "#", class: "button white icon star favorited"
        = link_to "Generate PDF", "#", class: "button white icon pdf"
        = link_to "Export Data", "#", class: "button white icon download"
    ~~~
